msgid "Spiritual Seekers and Mystics"
msgstr "Duhovni iskalci in mistiki"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Curious, introspective, open-minded, and drawn to "
"esoteric knowledge. They may have a strong interest in uncovering hidden "
"meanings or patterns in life. Occupations: Spiritual coaches, tarot readers,"
" astrologers, or individuals involved in New Age practices. Ideological "
"Spectrum: Likely to lean toward spiritual or metaphysical beliefs. They may "
"see the tools as a way to connect with deeper truths or universal energies."
msgstr ""
"Značilnosti osebnosti: Radovedni, introspektivni, odprti, ter privlači "
"esoterično znanje. Morda imajo močan interes za odkrivanje skritih pomenov "
"ali vzorcev v življenju. Poklici: duhovni trenerji, taborljenci tarot, "
"astrolozi ali posamezniki, ki se ukvarjajo z New Age praksami. Ideološki "
"spekter: verjetno se nagnajo k duhovnim ali metafizičnim prepričanjem. Morda"
" vidijo orodja kot način povezovanja z globljimi resnicami ali univerzalnimi"
" energijami."

msgid "Numerologists and Gematria Enthusiasts"
msgstr "Numerologi in Gematria navdušenci"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Analytical, detail-oriented, and fascinated by the "
"relationship between numbers and language. They may enjoy decoding symbolic "
"meanings. Occupations: Freelance numerologists, writers on esoteric topics, "
"or hobbyists exploring numerology. Ideological Spectrum: May range from "
"those who view numerology as a fun intellectual exercise to those who "
"believe in its profound spiritual significance."
msgstr ""
"Značilnosti osebnosti: Analitični, osredotočeni na podrobnosti, in navdušeni"
" nad odnosom med številkami in jezikom. Morda uživajo v dešifriranju "
"simboličnih pomenov. Poklici: samostojni numerologi, pisatelji o esoteričnih"
" temah ali hobisti, ki raziskujejo numerologijo. Ideološki spekter: Lahko se"
" giblje od tistih, ki številologijo vidijo kot zabavno intelektualno vajo, "
"do tistih, ki verjamejo v njeno globoko duhovno bistvo."

msgid "Historians and Linguists"
msgstr "Historiki in lingvistiki"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Scholarly, methodical, and interested in historical or "
"cultural contexts of numerical systems like Abjad. Occupations: Academics, "
"researchers, or students studying Middle Eastern languages, history, or "
"religious texts. Ideological Spectrum: Likely to approach the tools from a "
"secular, academic perspective, focusing on their historical or linguistic "
"significance."
msgstr ""
"Značilnosti osebnosti: Znanje, metodični in zainteresirani za zgodovinske "
"ali kulturne kontekste numeričnih sistemov, kot je Abjad. Poklici: "
"akademiki, raziskovalci ali študenti, ki preučujejo jezike Bližnjega vzhoda,"
" zgodovino ali verske besede. Ideološki spekter: verjetno pristopajo k "
"orodjem iz sekularne, akademske perspektive, osredotočeni na njihovo "
"zgodovinsko ali jezikovno bistvo."

msgid "Religious or Faith-Based Individuals"
msgstr "Religiozni ali veroizpovedni posamezniki"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Devout, reflective, and seeking deeper connections to "
"their faith. They may use the tools to explore religious texts or divine "
"messages. Occupations: Religious scholars, imams, priests, or laypeople with"
" a strong interest in their faith’s mystical traditions. Ideological "
"Spectrum: Likely to have a traditional or conservative worldview, using the "
"tools to reinforce their spiritual beliefs."
msgstr ""
"Značilnosti osebnosti: Pobožni, razmišljajoči in iščejo globlje povezave z "
"njihovo vero. Morda uporabljajo orodja za raziskovanje verskih besedil ali "
"božanskih sporočil. Poklici: verski učenjaki, imami, sveti ali prosti ljudje"
" z močnim zanimanjem za mistične tradicije svoje vere. Ideološki spekter: "
"verjetno imajo tradicionalni ali konzervativni svetopisem, ki uporablja "
"orodja za okrepitev svojih duhovnih prepričanj."

msgid "Writers and Artists"
msgstr "Pisatelji in umetniki"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Creative, imaginative, and drawn to symbolic or abstract"
" concepts. They may use the tools for inspiration or to add layers of "
"meaning to their work. Occupations: Authors, poets, visual artists, or "
"musicians. Ideological Spectrum: May range from secular creatives to those "
"with a spiritual or mystical bent."
msgstr ""
"Značilnosti osebnosti: Ustvarjalni, domišljijski in privlači simbolične ali "
"abstraktne koncepte. Morda uporabljajo orodja za navdih ali za dodajanje "
"plasti pomena svojemu delu. Poklici: avtorji, pesniki, vizualni umetniki ali"
" glasbeniki. Ideološki spekter: Lahko se giblje od sekularnih ustvarjalcev "
"do tistih z duhovnim ali mističnim prepričanjem."

msgid "Puzzle and Riddle Enthusiasts"
msgstr "Navdušenci nad ugankami in ugibami"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Playful, intellectually curious, and enjoy solving "
"complex problems or decoding patterns. Occupations: Hobbyists, puzzle "
"designers, or educators. Ideological Spectrum: Likely to approach the tools "
"as a form of entertainment or mental exercise, with little ideological "
"attachment."
msgstr ""
"Značilnosti osebnosti: Veselo, intelektualno radovedno in uživa v reševanju "
"zapletenih problemov ali dešifriranju vzorcev. Poklici: hobisti, oblikovalci"
" ugank ali izobraževalci. Ideološki spekter: verjetno pristopajo k orodjem "
"kot obliki zabave ali mentalnega vaje, z malo ideološkega pripadanja."

msgid "Conspiracy Theorists and Alternative Thinkers"
msgstr "Teoristi o konspiracijah in alternativni razmišljajoči"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Skeptical of mainstream narratives, drawn to uncovering "
"hidden truths or patterns in systems. Occupations: Independent researchers, "
"bloggers, or activists. Ideological Spectrum: May have a more radical or "
"unconventional worldview, using the tools to support alternative theories or"
" narratives."
msgstr ""
"Značilnosti osebnosti: Skeptični do glavnih zgodb, privlači jih odkrivanje "
"skritih resnic ali vzorcev v sistemih. Poklici: neodvisni raziskovalci, "
"blogerji ali aktivisti. Ideološki spekter: Lahko imajo bolj radikalni ali "
"neobičajni svetopisem, ki uporabljajo orodja za podporo alternativnim "
"teorijam ali zgodbam."

